  "diagram_type": "stateDiagram",
  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> Login: User Credentials\n    Login --> TokensGenerated: Success\n    \n    state TokensGenerated {\n        [*] --> AccessToken_Stateless\n        [*] --> RefreshToken_Stateful\n    }\n    \n    AccessToken_Stateless --> Active: valid for 15m\n    Active --> Expired: after 15m\n    Expired --> Refresh: use RefreshToken\n    \n    RefreshToken_Stateful --> StoredInDB: Active for 7d\n    StoredInDB --> Rotated: Refresh RPC called\n    Rotated --> DeletedFromDB: Old Token\n    Rotated --> StoredInDB: New Token Pair Issued\n    \n    StoredInDB --> Revoked: DeleteUser called\n    Revoked --> [*]\n    \n    Expired --> [*]\n",
  "content_size": 634,
  "collected_at": "2026-02-06T10:37:11.344273",
  "compilation_status": "success",
  "license": "other_source",
  "license_name": "Other Source (GitHub-based)",
  "compilation_error": "",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，描述用户登录后的双Token生命周期。核心是两个分支：AccessToken是无状态的，15分钟有效；RefreshToken是有状态的，存数据库里，7天有效。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Login",
        "TokensGenerated",
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以起点是用户凭据触发Login，成功后进入TokensGenerated状态。这个状态内部要展开吗？还是直接连到两个Token？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Login",
        "TokensGenerated",
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "TokensGenerated要展开成复合状态，里面同时产出AccessToken_Stateless和RefreshToken_Stateful。然后AccessToken走Active→Expired，Expired之后用RefreshToken去刷新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TokensGenerated",
        "AccessToken_Stateless",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful",
        "Active",
        "Expired",
        "Refresh"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了。AccessToken分支：Active状态标注15分钟有效，然后到Expired。RefreshToken分支我画了StoredInDB表示活跃状态。这里RefreshToken的流转需要细化吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Active",
        "Expired",
        "StoredInDB",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，RefreshToken_Stateful先到StoredInDB。然后有两个出口：一是调用Refresh RPC时进入Rotated，Rotated会产生新Token对并存回StoredInDB，同时旧Token要DeletedFromDB；二是调用DeleteUser时直接Revoked。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "StoredInDB",
        "Rotated",
        "DeletedFromDB",
        "Revoked",
        "RefreshToken_Stateful"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Rotated之后分出两条线，一条到DeletedFromDB标记Old Token，另一条回到StoredInDB标注New Token Pair Issued。Revoked和DeletedFromDB都应该是终点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Rotated",
        "DeletedFromDB",
        "StoredInDB",
        "Revoked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，还有Expired状态也要能结束。另外Rotated到StoredInDB的迁移标注要清楚写\"New Token Pair Issued\"，避免和初始生成混淆。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Expired",
        "Rotated",
        "StoredInDB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部调整完毕。现在Expired可以走到终点，Rotated到StoredInDB的标注也已更新。整个状态机覆盖了登录、Token生成、AccessToken失效、RefreshToken轮换和吊销的完整流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Expired",
        "Rotated",
        "StoredInDB",
        "DeletedFromDB",
        "Revoked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
